    <h1>Hi, I'm Evan</h1>
    <p>My name is Evan, I am a graduate of <a class="link" style="font-weight:bold" target="_blank" href="https://www.insead.edu/">INSEAD</a> (MBA class of 21D)
      and I'm also the co-founder of Centroly, a social network for collecting and sharing new ideas.
        I previously worked as a Technical Program Manager at <a class="link" style="font-weight:bold" target="_blank" href="https://www.grab.com/">Grab</a>, a super-app unicorn in Southeast Asia, 
        and was also Chief of Staff at a data analytics software-as-a service startup.
    <p>Having worked with many startups making a difference through building great products and deploying data, I enjoy finding
      ways to use software and data to help action-takers operationalise their visions, to do meaningful work
      and build purposeful careers.
    <p> I coded this site on Ruby using Middleman Blog and GitHub Pages.
    </p>
